@startuml
actor "Desarrollador" as Dev
participant "GitHub Codespaces\n(VS Code)" as CS
node "DevContainer\n(service: app)" as DC
database "PostgreSQL\n(db_postgres)" as PG
database "MariaDB\n(db_mariadb)" as MA

Dev -> CS: Abre workspace (sin Docker local)
CS -> DC: Provisiona contenedor via docker-compose
DC -> PG: Healthcheck + migraciones usando credenciales .env
DC -> MA: Healthcheck + pruebas de conectividad
DC -> Dev: Expone 8000/5432/3306 para debugging y SQLTools
@enduml
